{"tid":523912,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經] 結婚與埋單的分別","createTime":"2018-01-09T05:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T09:50:42.000Z","uid":78016,"like":24,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb4ec49762c6ca7daaf1ff35ec4717436aa111b","tid":523912,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:05:51.000Z","msg":"有鑑於好多巴打都唔清楚兩者分別 再宣傳下結婚同埋單的定義<br />\n<br />\n結婚(Marriage)定義係女方結婚時係處女或者除左新朗外無同其他人做過愛<br />\n<br />\n埋單(Bill, please)定義係女方結婚時非處女<strong>而且</strong>同過兩個或以上嘅男人做愛<br />\n<br />\n補充一點 我只係講出個定義<br />\n如果無得揀男士只能幫人埋單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男士有得揀緊係想結婚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個post 只有 未食過處的男士,老婆處唔係自己破的男士, 臭西會負評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793a75a913a0599d49a9f3ce44ab2a7ae5b0a9e6","tid":523912,"uid":120850,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:07:29.000Z","msg":"咁男人唔係處而又同過兩個女人做又叫唔叫埋單"},{"pid":"61746c73bf5ad054287d0738a002d3af4237f19f","tid":523912,"uid":78016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"793a75a913a0599d49a9f3ce44ab2a7ae5b0a9e6","tid":523912,"uid":120850,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:07:29.000Z","msg":"咁男人唔係處而又同過兩個女人做又叫唔叫埋單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:10:03.000Z","msg":"香港女人有無同香港男人求婚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見好多人都係女逼個男嘅娶佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6378a1eb568c21a27746b1a0d5bc4f4cd6a0ba35","tid":523912,"uid":78016,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"如果女人會跪地同個男求婚, 俾酒席錢 有樓有車<br />\n咁個女人要求個男係處或者可以諗下合唔合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602398dc4375e259ac272a49827e04f4b5fe53cd","tid":523912,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T0